msgstr "Google TTS For NVDA 無法朗讀此文字。"

msgid "Google TTS For NVDA could not start its local browser bridge."
msgstr "Google TTS For NVDA 無法啟動其本機瀏覽器橋接程式。"

msgid "Google TTS For NVDA could not start speech in the Chromium browser runtime."
msgstr "Google TTS For NVDA 無法在 Chromium 瀏覽器執行階段中開始語音朗讀。"

msgid "Google TTS For NVDA is already checking for updates."
msgstr "Google TTS For NVDA 已在檢查更新中。"

msgid "Google TTS For NVDA is not connected to the Chromium browser runtime."
msgstr "Google TTS For NVDA 尚未連線至 Chromium 瀏覽器執行階段。"

msgid "Google TTS For NVDA is up to date. Current version: {version}."
msgstr "Google TTS For NVDA 已是最新版本。目前版本: {version}。"

msgid ""
"Google TTS For NVDA is using the selected Chromium browser runtime now. To change it safely, switch to another synthesizer first.\n"
"\n"
"Choose OK to open Select Synthesizer. Choose Cancel to keep the current Chromium browser runtime."
msgstr ""
"Google TTS For NVDA 目前正在使用所選取的 Chromium 瀏覽器執行階段。若要安全地變更它，請先切換至其他合成器。\n"
"\n"
"選擇「確定」以開啟「選擇合成器」。選擇「取消」以保留目前的 Chromium 瀏覽器執行階段。"

