msgid "Google TTS For NVDA updates cannot be installed in the Windows Store version of NVDA."
msgstr "無法在 Windows 市集版本的 NVDA 中安裝 Google TTS For NVDA 更新。"

msgid "Google TTS For NVDA will use {runtime} as its Chromium browser runtime."
msgstr "Google TTS For NVDA 將使用 {runtime} 作為其 Chromium 瀏覽器執行階段。"

