msgid ""
"Microsoft Edge is available, but Microsoft Edge WebView2 Runtime is not available.\n"
"\n"
"Google TTS For NVDA needs WebView2 when Microsoft Edge is the Chromium browser runtime. NVDA will keep using the previous synthesizer until WebView2 is installed.\n"
"\n"
"Choose Download online installer to download Microsoft's Evergreen Bootstrapper. Choose Open Microsoft WebView2 page if you need an offline installer or a fixed-version package."
msgstr ""
"Microsoft Edge 可用，但 Microsoft Edge WebView2 執行階段不可用。\n"
"\n"
"當 Chromium 瀏覽器執行階段為 Microsoft Edge 時，Google TTS For NVDA 需要 WebView2。在安裝 WebView2 之前，NVDA 將繼續使用先前的合成器。\n"
"\n"
"選擇「下載線上安裝程式」以下載 Microsoft 的 Evergreen 安裝小幫手。若您需要離線安裝程式或固定版本套件，請選擇「開啟 Microsoft WebView2 頁面」。"

msgid "Microsoft Edge was found, but Microsoft Edge WebView2 Runtime was not found. Keeping the current Google TTS For NVDA Chromium browser runtime setting."
msgstr "已找到 Microsoft Edge，但未找到 Microsoft Edge WebView2 執行階段。將保留目前 Google TTS For NVDA 的 Chromium 瀏覽器執行階段設定。"

msgid "Microsoft Edge WebView2 Runtime is needed"
msgstr "需要 Microsoft Edge WebView2 執行階段"

msgid "Microsoft Edge WebView2 Runtime was not found. Install it before using Microsoft Edge as the Google TTS For NVDA Chromium browser runtime."
msgstr "未找到 Microsoft Edge WebView2 執行階段。請先安裝後，再將 Microsoft Edge 用作 Google TTS For NVDA 的 Chromium 瀏覽器執行階段。"

msgid "Microsoft Edge WebView2 Runtime was not found. Install or repair Microsoft Edge WebView2 Runtime before using Microsoft Edge as the Google TTS For NVDA Chromium browser runtime."
msgstr "未找到 Microsoft Edge WebView2 執行階段。請先安裝或修復 Microsoft Edge WebView2 執行階段，再將 Microsoft Edge 用作 Google TTS For NVDA 的 Chromium 瀏覽器執行階段。"

