msgid ""
"Version 0.5:\n"
"- Added built-in add-on update checking, with optional startup checks, localized update information, in-NVDA download, handoff to NVDA's add-on installer, and support for small hotfix builds inside the same public version.\n"
"- Improved Chrome, Edge, and Brave runtime fallback, including skipping Edge when WebView2 is missing and another supported runtime is usable, and reducing silent startup or connection failures while the browser is still starting.\n"
"- Improved NVDA compatibility, language-change handling, speech reliability, optional pause shortening, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, and Russian localization, and accessible read-only status fields."
msgstr ""
"版本 0.5:\n"
"- 新增內建的附加元件更新檢查功能，可選擇於啟動時自動檢查、查看在地化的更新資訊、直接在 NVDA 內下載、移交給 NVDA 的附加元件安裝程式進行安裝，並支援同一公開版本內的小型修補版本。\n"
"- 改善了 Chrome、Edge 及 Brave 執行階段的回退機制，包括在缺少 WebView2 且有其他受支援的執行階段可用時自動略過 Edge，以及在瀏覽器仍在啟動時等待並重試，減少靜默啟動失敗或連線失敗。\n"
"- 改善了與 NVDA 的相容性、語言變更處理、語音朗讀穩定性、可選的縮短停頓功能、簡體中文、正體中文與俄文在地化，並改善唯讀狀態欄位的無障礙存取。"

